The Platform (Charter compiler, Ledger, Fleet API, and console GUI) depends on
blastcontain-core (Apache-2.0) for shared types, signing, and the Charter
schema, and uses blastcontain-guard (Apache-2.0) in its closed-loop
integration tests. Runtime dependencies (FastAPI, uvicorn, SQLAlchemy,
PyYAML, Next.js for the GUI) are not vendored here — record their provenance
and licenses in your own deployment's AIBOM.
